    "direction": "Consider investigating the factors that led to the increase in ad spending during March and the subsequent drop in April. Assess whether these changes align with sales cycles or specific marketing campaigns.",
    "action": "Conduct a detailed analysis comparing monthly ad spend against key performance indicators such as sales data and conversion rates during the same period. Run a query to calculate monthly conversion rates and sales figures: SELECT strftime('%Y-%m', OrderDate) AS month, SUM(SalesAmount) AS total_sales, AVG(ConversionRate) AS avg_conversion_rate FROM data GROUP BY month ORDER BY month;"
