Profit_Derivation_Insight.insight_summary:
{
    "insight": "The Profit column does not consistently equal the SalesAmount minus Cost. The discrepancies suggest that there might be additional factors, like discounts or other costs, contributing to the profit calculation.",
    "direction": "Investigate other contributors to the profit calculation, such as potential overlooked costs or revenue adjustments like discounts and returns, to understand these discrepancies better.",
    "action": "Run a query to include the Discount column and other potential overheads to recalculate profit accurately. Consider: SELECT OrderID, SalesAmount, Cost, Discount, Profit, (SalesAmount - Cost - Discount) AS recalculated_profit FROM data WHERE Profit != (SalesAmount - Cost - Discount) LIMIT 5."
}

